creator: Cito Cabs
descriptionHtml:
The Cito Cab app offers a platform to cab agents & Cab drivers. The Cab Agent can publish the ride with all required details and driver can pick the ride published by the agent.

We are offering the rides from more than 15 states all across India.Driver can view the all states rides in one place and also view the ride according to state wise.

Here’s how it works:
• An agent can add ride within India with some required details like Pickup City,Destination City,Car type,Fare,Contact No.
• The driver can view the ride and contact the agent or customer directly via the mobile number.

For the drivers,they have to purchase subscription 0f 249 Rupees(Included All Taxes) which will be valid for one month.We will also give the feature of rewards for referral to other driver in upcoming app update.

For any queries or questions,You may reach us @sharmabajajcito@gmail.com
